WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.137 --> 00:00:03.417
[MUSIC]

00:00:03.417 --> 00:00:06.328
Men uzoqroq boraman deb o‘ylayman
Men bo‘lganimda, deb aytish uchun qaytib

00:00:06.328 --> 00:00:08.290
magistrlik dissertatsiyasini bajarish.

00:00:08.290 --> 00:00:13.000
Effektlar haqida bilardim
tilning yo‘qolishi va

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.740
uning borligi sababli
mening shaxsimni olish.

00:00:17.060 --> 00:00:20.470
Miwok bo‘lish va bilmaslik
tili yoki urf-odatlari,

00:00:20.470 --> 00:00:26.650
Men bu so‘zni bilmasligim kerakligini his qildim
bo‘lishi mumkin, bilasiz, etarli emas.

00:00:26.650 --> 00:00:31.610
Bilasizmi, men haqimda ko‘p narsa bilmayman
meros, mening madaniyatim va men xohlayman

00:00:31.610 --> 00:00:34.900
ko‘proq bilish va men o‘tishni istayman
bu bilimlar mening bolalarimga berilgan.

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:39.307
Shunday qilib, men savatga qaray boshladim
tilni ozgina to‘quv.

00:00:39.307 --> 00:00:43.255
Men bilan intervyu boshladim
buvim va onam va

00:00:43.255 --> 00:00:48.467
ko‘proq ma’lumot olishga harakat qilaman
eng yaqin oila a’zolarimdan.

00:00:48.467 --> 00:00:51.827
[MUSIC]

00:00:51.827 --> 00:00:56.807
Ammo keyin men shunday veb-saytni topdim
qabila a’zolaridan biri tomonidan qurilgan va

00:00:56.807 --> 00:01:02.360
unda sanashning ba’zi audio lavhalari bor edi,
ranglar va shunga o‘xshash narsalar.

00:01:02.360 --> 00:01:06.548
Va men o‘ynay boshladim
mening o‘g‘lim bilan va

00:01:06.548 --> 00:01:11.260
biz raqamlarni bosamiz va
keyingisini bosishdan oldin

00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:15.228
kutib turing, shunday deyishga harakat qilaman
Men buni to‘g‘ri va ayta olamanmi, bilib olaman

00:01:15.228 --> 00:01:19.520
u xuddi o‘yin kabi o‘tdi
o‘g‘lim va men o‘ynadik.

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:22.520
Va shu bilan ko‘proq narsani qilishni xohladim

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:25.720
Men juda ko‘p oilalar ekanligini angladim
biz ham xuddi shunday vaziyatdamiz.

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:26.980
Bay Bay hududidamiz,

00:01:26.980 --> 00:01:31.690
bu taxminan ikki soatlik masofada joylashgan
qabilalar jamoasidan.

00:01:31.690 --> 00:01:34.520
Va agar ko‘proq odamlar bo‘lsa
uzoq bo‘lganlar,

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:38.020
ularga kirish mumkin emas, shuning uchun
tilni xalqqa etkazaylik.

